{"tid":1239044,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】唯唯梁競徽衝出國際　惡搞受傷照登Euronews片段","createTime":"2019-06-18T04:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T11:24:49.000Z","uid":49391,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cf794056f8d59d1a40c4e3230c444dcff3d09b1d","tid":1239044,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpouP25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpouP25.jpg&h=40863a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁競徽（原名梁烈唯）最近在網上人氣高企，香港的「反修例」遊行中多次「被出現」，雖然唯唯早己在微博公開澄清，指自己並沒有參加遊行，不過一眾網民依然少理，繼續封他為「英雄」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJ9Bu25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJ9Bu25.jpg&h=1c10c1d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連登網民的改圖，圈住徽徽正參與遊行。（連登討論區圖片）<br />\n<br />\n一連串惡搞事件後，在昨日的遊行當中，甚至有人將唯唯的樣子印成海報，於街上派發。有市民在遊行期間，高舉唯唯的樣子，並且被不少人拍下片段。到今日，在外國媒體&mdash;歐洲新聞台（Euronews）報道香港情況時，竟然將這段片報一併報道，並用將唯唯的頭近鏡，人人都看得十分清楚。Euronews是一個全球播放的新聞頻道，唯唯間接進入了全球人的眼光，相信連他自己也估不到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6MtbiWL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6MtbiWL.jpg&h=960c0bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEuronews報道出遊行事件，更出現梁競徽的大頭照。（Euronews螢幕截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7GL5ooz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GL5ooz.jpg&h=a9a94ca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民改咗唔少圖，連三哥都中招。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/341670/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F341670%2F&d=b2hjM7c23Ds3Tm%2B3KbcyAQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=64857191\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/341670/</a>"},{"pid":"dc26ec778e400f83a2aa057cb1c161298b24bf01","tid":1239044,"uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yHN7whu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyHN7whu.gif&h=5046238b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69aac2b285198929abcd71a877713aac20723d62","tid":1239044,"uid":228360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"唯唯！"}]}